</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-id1168046019878">
<problem id="fs-id1168048740201">
<para id="fs-id1168048296996">Describe the main differences between C-type and S-type asteroids.</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-id1168048250756">
<problem id="fs-id1168046063114">
<para id="fs-id1168048781543">In addition to the ones mentioned in <link target-id="fs-id1168046019878"/>, what is the third, rarer class of asteroids?</para>
