</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-id1168048781539">
<problem id="fs-id1168048733236">
<para id="fs-id1168048549539">Compare asteroids of the asteroid belt with Earth-approaching asteroids. What is the main difference between the two groups?</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-id1168048594368">
<problem id="fs-id1168048242067">
<para id="fs-id1168048543641">Briefly describe NASA’s Spaceguard Survey. How many objects have been found in this survey?</para>
